Scott Shirley, his wife Mayo and son Phoenix were travelling back from Disney World to Washington DC on a United Airlines flight . 
  Family discovered their luggage was wet with vomit on the floor of the cabin . 
  Mr Shirley says staff refused to clean the affected area before take-off . 
  Family were offered a $150 flight voucher or to fly the next day . 
  United Airlines has apologised to the family for the incident . 
 